						<summary>

						<p>Slab setup near <hi rend="italic">Pīrala Chāvadi.</hi></p>						

						<p>Vijayanagara: Sadāśiva.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1466, Krōdhi, Bhādrapada śu. 11,</hi> corresponding to 1544 A.D., August 28, Thursday.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. It seems to register a gift of land to the temples of Mallikārjuna, Kaṁnīśvara, Vīrabhadradēva and others by Koṁḍōju-ayyadēva-Mahārāju, Malrāju ayyadēva-Mahārāju and mahāmaṇḍalēśvara Gōbbūri Narasarājayya from their <hi rend="italic">amaram</hi> fields in the Kamdanavōli-sīma.</p>						

						</summary>
